          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">Trump‚Äôs special gift</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
         <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;">
         <strong>Summary: Qatar‚Äôs luxury jet proposal raised accusations of bribery and corruption against the Trump administration.</strong>
         </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
          Donald Trump‚Äôs interest in accepting a $400M luxury Boeing 747-8 jet from <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-13-may-25-spotlight-h2-4-qatar-s-royal-family" target="_blank">Qatar's royal family</a> has sparked a judicial and political firestorm. This jet was intended to be a temporary Air Force One replacement and later a gift to his presidential library foundation.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
          While Trump‚Äôs attorney general concluded that it is ‚Äúlegally permissible‚Äù to accept the luxury gifts, critics argue it violates the Constitution‚Äôs <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-13-may-25-spotlight-h2-5-emoluments-clause" target="_blank">Emoluments Clause</a>. This clause bars US officials from accepting gifts from foreign states without Congressional approval.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
       Meanwhile, the Democrats and watchdog groups warn about foreign influence. They call the agreement unprecedented and potentially corrupt. Other political spectrums have also shown distaste because of Qatar‚Äôs engagements with militant groups like Hamas and Hezbollah.</p>
       <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
      Senator Chuck Schumer and Representative Jamie Raskin labeled it an affront to ‚ÄúAmerica First‚Äù and a constitutional breach. The timing raised concerns, as this follows a <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-13-may-25-spotlight-h2-6-5-5b-trump-organization-agreement" target="_blank">$5.5B Trump Organization agreement</a> in Qatar. Irrespective of Trump‚Äôs decision, this incident will increase scrutiny of his ties with foreign powers.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
